      "Title": "Zaya.Primitives.LocalizedException",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"docs/api/Zaya.Primitives.LocalizedException.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Base class for exceptions that carry a localizable user-facing message.\nSubclasses override <xref href=\"Zaya.Primitives.LocalizedException.GetLocalizedMessage(System.Globalization.CultureInfo)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to resolve translations.\nThe constructor receives only a localization key; the default culture resource file is the source of strings.</p>\n"
    },
