      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Zaya.Primitives.LocalizedString",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"docs/api/Zaya.Primitives.LocalizedString.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Represents a string that can be localized. Supports two modes:</p>\n<ul><li>Localized via a resolver function (typically a .resx <code>ResourceManager</code>).</li><li>Invariant — created via <xref href=\"Zaya.Primitives.LocalizedString.Invariant(System.String)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and never translated.</li></ul>\n<p sourcefile=\"docs/api/Zaya.Primitives.LocalizedString.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"5\">All source strings live in resource files; no English defaults are embedded in code.</p>\n"
    },
