      "Title": "Zaya.Primitives.SettingDescriptor",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"docs/api/Zaya.Primitives.SettingDescriptor.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Abstract base class for describing a configurable engine setting.\nSubclasses carry type-specific properties (e.g. <xref href=\"Zaya.Primitives.StringSettingDescriptor.MinLength\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>,\n<xref href=\"Zaya.Primitives.IntegerSettingDescriptor.MinValue\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>, <xref href=\"Zaya.Primitives.EnumSettingDescriptor.Options\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>).\nHosts use pattern matching on the concrete type to render the appropriate UI control.</p>\n"
    },
